                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "First reaction: Hooray! This paper asks a vital question: \"What is Programming?\". The discussion of possible answers to this question is quite interesting. I might have a different view of what programming is, but, that doesn't matter as much as just having the question verbalized and seeing a discussion ensue."
                            }
